                                                    <li>Collaborating with the head of story</li>
                                                    <li>Creating the dramatic structure of the screenplay, ensuring that it has a 1st, 2nd, and 3rd act.</li>
                                                    <li>Supporting the head of the story in creating the background for the story - developing ideas together</li>
                                                    <li>The scope of the actual screen writing should be divided between the head of the story and the screenwriter</li>
                                                </ul>
                                            
