                                                    <p class="description">The DIT is responsible for managing, transferring, securing, and backing up all the digital data acquired on-set. They must keep track of where the footage and audio is stored, and ensure that the editors have the files they need in order to edit together the dailies, and later, the film.</p>
                                                
